-- General Growth Wins Bankruptcy Court Leave to Refinance $400 Million Loan
-- Tiffany Kary
-- 2010-07-22T14:38:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-22/general-growth-wins-bankruptcy-court-leave-to-refinance-400-million-loan.html

          
          
             General Growth Properties Inc., the
second-largest U.S. mall operator, won permission to refinance a
$400 million loan to fund operations in bankruptcy, saving the
company $2.7 million a month in interest payments.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
